  <p><a id="TSJN-01-03-0643-kw-0001" class="keywordref" title="jump to My last letter to you in text" href="#TSJN-01-03-0643-ks-0001">My last letter to you</a>: The last on record is that <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-03-02-0607" class="document">dated 4 Aug. 1780</a>. On Gates <a id="TSJN-01-03-0643-kw-0002" class="keywordref" title="jump to Proclamations in text" href="#TSJN-01-03-0643-ks-0901">Proclamations</a>, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-03-02-0604" class="document">Gates letter to TJ of 3 Aug.</a></p></div>
